						<summary>

						<p>Registers a gift of land by purchase to Vaikunda-dāsar (vide No. 268 by <hi rend="bold">Kamalādēvī,</hi> a queen of <hi rend="bold">Vīra-Rāmanātha,</hi> for her own merit. This record also probably belongs to the <hi rend="bold">8th regnal year</hi> of the king.</p>						

